# Version Control & CI/CD (Keep out of Docker context for security and speed)
.git
**/.git
.github
**/.github
.husky
**/.husky

# Dependencies (Docker must install its own OS-specific dependencies)
node_modules
**/node_modules

# Build Outputs & Caches (Docker must build fresh)
.next
**/.next
dist
**/dist
.turbo
**/.turbo
*.tsbuildinfo
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Documentation & Misc (Not needed at runtime, wastes image size)
docs/
**/docs/
README.md
LICENSE
docker.compose.yml

# Testing & Logs
coverage
**/coverage
*.log
**/*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*

# Environment & Local Data (CRITICAL: Prevents secrets from leaking into image layers)
.env*
!.env.example
uploads/
**/uploads/
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
*.pem
